    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/2a127d76c4b8cbc09d82da5eaac40040.avif?t=1771622667\" alt=\"Deliver Soup\" width=1024 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/f3192ca5b82e2dec9ad9c36309bb9f74.poster.avif?t=1771622667\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/f3192ca5b82e2dec9ad9c36309bb9f74.webm?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/f3192ca5b82e2dec9ad9c36309bb9f74.mp4?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Our customers are craving some soup, can't leave them hanging can we? Go around town at night delivering soup to our customer's homes until they are satisfied. If they get hooked, and they will, you will be returning the following nights to share more of our wonderful soup!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more and faster you deliver, the more money you will make. So make sure to give everyone a taste, and soon they will all be <strong>thanking you for the soup</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/a5895d420b4fb7257a6a7f4bf65c67b8.avif?t=1771622667\" alt=\"Day &amp;amp; Night\" width=1024 height=76 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/dff2a018c4e4ffc69fad98c6b0e23a18.poster.avif?t=1771622667\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/dff2a018c4e4ffc69fad98c6b0e23a18.webm?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/dff2a018c4e4ffc69fad98c6b0e23a18.mp4?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You deliver soup from 5pm to 1am, outside of those hours are considered your own free time. You can fill in those hours however you want. Explore and find secrets. Go around shopping. Decorate your home. Go gambling. Or simply relax at home with your cat. Fill in those hours however you'd like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just remember to stay out of the kitchen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/23b0b355febaccbf519091fd0726f5ec.avif?t=1771622667\" alt=\"Food &amp;amp; Sleep\" width=1024 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/e40c0fc689ed1fac17d4331bb0ce224e.poster.avif?t=1771622667\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/e40c0fc689ed1fac17d4331bb0ce224e.webm?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/e40c0fc689ed1fac17d4331bb0ce224e.mp4?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Unfortunately, we cannot be out delivering soup all day. So make sure to get all the rest and proteins you may need outside of working hours. Only a healthy deliverer will be able to satisfy our customers. The local shops are open during the day, so feel free to get your fill out of them when you can. That way you can perform at peak performance during your deliveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/5f2548c905c9b9fafaa73f53155cecf8.avif?t=1771622667\" alt=\"Bicycle Upgrades\" width=1024 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/749bc9da7eedaf7838c14204cb3e8161.poster.avif?t=1771622667\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/749bc9da7eedaf7838c14204cb3e8161.webm?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2132610/extras/749bc9da7eedaf7838c14204cb3e8161.mp4?t=1771622667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>We have given you a bicycle to aid you in your delivery tasks, it's quite sturdy and can go pretty fast. However, there is still room for improvement. The local bicycle shop will be able to pimp up your bicycle to your liking, from styling it to turbo boosters, they have it all. Just make sure you have the funds to afford it all.</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 荷兰语, 印度尼西亚语, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 泰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
